✅ Added assignProjectsToEmployee in EmployeeController
✅ Added assignEmployeesToProject in ProjectController
✅ Updated DAO and DAOImpl to support fetching multiple records by IDs
✅ Implemented findByIds method in DAO for batch fetching

This makes the Employee-Project mapping fully functional! Let me know if you need any refinements.

